Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:36.05,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,480)}模仿和無意識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和亞城木君談過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是昨天的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為不去觸碰它反而更好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓他們覺得編輯部並沒有將此視作問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而更不能由我們來提起這個話題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被問起 我覺得只要一笑而過就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 不該讓他們看到我們過激的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最需要細心留意的是作家的精神面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了這點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個不是會因為這點事而氣餒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所說的話就最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 原稿 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩話完結的情人節故事  收尾不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接著下次討論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是和以前一樣 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個銀行搶劫的事件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「PCP」中已經提過會給保安公司和銀行添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編輯部甚至已經對一部分報導提出抗議了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以一切照常即可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像之前說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要作品中真他們所實行的完全犯罪有可行性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓孩子們想去模仿就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」不是助長犯罪的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是從主人公們的計劃策略陷阱等中獲得樂趣的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自連載開始就收到抗議的電話和信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但撇開這些 它已經成為了人氣漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是讀者理解我們的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這次的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全不可能動畫化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 「白色情人節大作戰」的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把這個作為NAME吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生 還在公司裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木的原作文章寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一點我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傳真給你 能不能看一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實這風格和之前有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 果然是受了那個事件的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 可能是因為我們目前一直擔心那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會出現這種錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先觀察段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他有意持續這風格我們再想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到我的漫畫動畫化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想要增加一個工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要個高水準的工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還有意復出的話 就到我這來工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福田君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能別再管我的事了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:06:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 平丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中井先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！中井？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼樹 全都是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}蒼樹 快給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優梨碳 我現在就趕過來 盡量爭取些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我等到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中井！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你碰優梨碳一根手指的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平！丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 優梨碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不能出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再纏著蒼樹小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是那個女人的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這根本是恩將仇報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了很多傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擾亂了你漫畫人生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為你對漫畫的執著不過如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼樹小姐和她的美麗沒有罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我會拼上我的性命來守護她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在你滿意之前揍我就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平丸先生 你完全沒有被打的理由 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 優梨碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是男人和男人之間的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打的話就打我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也應該是中井先生最希望的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 請揍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍到你滿意為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩將仇報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當初其實只剩下漫畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經賭上人生的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Hideout Door」連載的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了那個的現在的我已經一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道那是我自己的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已經沒有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我到底該怎麼活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫畫真是太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被編輯骗進這個行業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果最後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一失足就是無邊的黑暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年後十年後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我 到時候會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要到我那裡做助手啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中井先生可能就是我的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這個我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才聽到你說拼上性命守護她的時候就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把蒼樹托付給這個男人應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點兒臭屁 但還是謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}貌似是為了爭風吃醋打架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}好像終於有同伴來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}到底是幹什麼來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像兩個人都麻煩了警察一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後不知怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像成為平丸先生的助手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 中經先生到底在幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟吉田先生說下要好好監視他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周的本報是第8位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！第8位？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直是5位以內的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白色情人節那話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木君你從那一話開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻意迴避在「PCP」中加入犯罪元素了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是和往常一樣在寫故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你無意識中寫出了避免招惹問題的內容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你自己沒那麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腦卻擅自行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近一個月來的原作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯的改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這次會有意識地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫出讓他們不去模仿的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把你指出的地方全部修改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋~人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒有點反覆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先來跟你說聲晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子模仿「PCP」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是會不高興的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會教給他們什麼該模仿什麼不該模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶你是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直是第2位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保持住這個狀態哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 原稿我就拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2位和第1位差多少票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…應該有50票以上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50票啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從來沒關心過問卷調查什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話的NAME可能會晚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚一些？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你往常都很快所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次和往常不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是要得到第1位的NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我去東京我有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我成為JACK最受歡迎的作家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我結束一部我討厭的漫畫的權限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得…得到第1位？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要得到第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君 NAME還沒完成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間上已經很緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才高木把文章原稿拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去你那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫NAME吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 高木君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很累的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要事先準備後兩話的原作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還完全沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在家創作的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用討論了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原案已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫好了之後會拿過來看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是之前高木未採用的原作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個拿出來用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是已經走投無路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個明顯沒有之前的犀利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明情況的話應該能休息一周…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木也應該不想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延遲的部分我會填補的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」第12位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來從未出現過兩位數排名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續三周…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CROW」好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周和第1位差不到20票
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就要得第1位了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責的作品形勢大好卻那副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你還不是一樣 最近一臉陰沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為「PCP」狀態不理想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝杯咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束一部討厭的作品的權限？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你太大聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事只有我和編輯長兩個人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要對任何人說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前從不在意問卷調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼突然認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且就算是第1位也不等於就是JACK最受歡迎的作家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道新妻君作為亞城木粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得現在的「PCP」沒有讀的價值而想讓它完結？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周的速報已經出了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」目前13位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 估計這周「CROW」是第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是速報 但它和第2位差距不小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 你老實說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不過是新瓶裝老酒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作為一個故事還是很有條理的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有時間了 這次就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人你覺得這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君 日程已經很緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作畫的時間也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木要干的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我熬夜個3天也沒任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我這就回家去寫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要寫出真城認同的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木君已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使快到期限
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木也一定會寫出讓人認可的原作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會畫出最好的畫稿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相使出全力協助對方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是亞城木夢葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高信任我等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了最高 為了亞城木夢葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次放置在金庫中的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與連載於週刊少年JACK上的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP完美犯罪黨」中的主人公一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留有PCP的字樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方認為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs30\pos(692,166)\c&HFDFDFD&\3c&H3D3E40&}到此一遊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}這和前幾日的金庫入侵事件很可能是同一嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部 好好支持亞城木君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木君怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他還沒和我聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事件他就受了那麼大的精神打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你們不原意 但也考慮考慮休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}至少這名犯人在看這部漫畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得寫原作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}是啊 是啊 可以說是模仿犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和真城說一下 今天休息比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一個人待著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 …
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也把飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了讓我一個人待著！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」目前第11位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 估計這周「CROW」是第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城打來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您撥打的用戶暫時無法接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 消沉到連我的電話都不接了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 香耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人現在的狀況接不了電話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看到了新聞以後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就馬上說要寫原作 讓他一個人待著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木第一次這麼跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說要一個人待著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經什麼忙都幫不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為那次盜竊事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要寫上PCP這幾個字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明PCP根本不會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 PCP絕對不會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是六塚君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把從別人那裡偷來的教科書藏在體育倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 這樣當然會讓人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是PCP 絕對不會藏在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候發現犯人是我而不是PCP的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六塚君發出預告書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事件發生就會被人認為是PCP干的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你本來是打算模仿他們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一開始就明白不是PCP所為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們不會偷別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不會給別人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切照計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功勞都轉給明知了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我估計明知也能很快發現不是PCP干的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯法就淪為了罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪誰都會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們的手法可是別人學不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~真超酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周的「PCP」太過癮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子上升了3位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓模仿犯替罪真是明智的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還收到了很多表揚的粉絲信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」不是助長犯罪的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓人明白這是什麼漫畫 我們該做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓模仿犯替罪 並創作否定其行為的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和高木都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.79,0:22:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這組合還是一如既往的合拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這回盡給真城添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作畫的日程很緊張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.73,0:22:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是亞城木夢葉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻君這周也是第１位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是英二 差距又拉大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但是不管差距如何拉大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要追上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:59.06,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}在不斷奮鬥的過程中最棒的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:03.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}讓它成形的那一刻令倍加珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:08.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}好似戰鬥 又彷彿聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:12.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}感覺（互相交織）  如此刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:17.41,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}所以更加努力奮鬥吧 保持自己的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:22.50,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（未來） 肯定就在這條延續下去的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:27.54,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}信念各不相同的夥伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:32.09,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Rival…and Friend！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.30,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}互相碰撞的Pride
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:43.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}無法讓步 今後仍將繼續貫徹自己的作法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:45.90,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}準備已經完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:50.36,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}一口氣追上去所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:53.53,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}永不放棄的 Pride
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:24:01.91,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}拼盡全力 因為喜歡所以在心中培養這份好感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:06.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}雖然不知道等待我們的會是怎樣的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.84,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（明天）我還是會（盡可能的）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:12.55,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻君說出了不得了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.96,0:24:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想做有損形象的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也太極端了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 連續和阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.98,0:24:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護夢想必須貫徹自己的做法
